{"tid":520001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SOGO外攔巴士打途人 警3個月後拘涉案男女","createTime":"2018-01-05T03:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T05:02:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a17a7141990635ea29e0f60993932f55a138c673","tid":520001,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一對男女於去年10月於銅鑼灣馬路間攔截巴士，造成交通擠塞，期間有途人上前阻止時，更被攔路男騎在身上扭打。警方經3個月的深入調查後，昨日於灣仔區拘捕涉案的兩名男女，分別涉嫌在公眾地方造成阻礙及普通襲擊。案件將於下周五東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n事發在去年10月6日晚上，據悉該對男女於銅鑼灣崇光百貨公司對開，擬乘搭2X線新巴往筲箕灣愛秩序灣，期間二人疑未能及時登車，突然情緒激動衝出馬路攔巴士。根據當時的片段所見，兩名男女途人見狀走出馬路，向攔路情侶出言勸止，但雙方言語不合觸發衝突，攔路男與熱心男途人發生推撞，男途人繼而倒地，遭攔路男騎在身上，並發生扭打，車上乘客都「嘩」聲四起。其後兩人停手，並各自起身站於巴士旁。<br />\n<br />\n其後有警員接報到場調查，新巴隨後駛離現場，疑曾動手惡男與熱心男途人，雙方願意和解，涉事男女亦獲准離去。<br />\n<br />\n不過警方經深入調查後，昨日於灣仔區拘捕一名29歲姓王的男子，以及一名31歲姓伍女子，涉嫌「在公眾地方造成阻礙」。其中王男亦涉嫌「普通襲擊」。"},{"pid":"5ca274c97dbd303b17544d2ba47b335615c84314","tid":520001,"uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"於3個月前，銅鑼灣發生躁夫妻攔巴士犯眾怒事件，警方經詳細調查後，昨日在灣仔區將該對夫妻拘捕，2人均被控涉嫌在公眾地方造成阻礙，而男子更加控涉嫌普通襲擊罪，將於本月12日在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n涉案男子姓王(29歲)，其妻姓伍(31歲)。於去年(2017年)10月6日晚上11時許，2人在軒尼詩道崇光百貨對開，被指疑因「送車尾」，強行將一輛2X線新巴攔截，導致交通受影響擠塞，有市民挺身理論，反遭指罵及遭推撞，警員到場調查後，將事件列為糾紛處理，涉事夫妻亦獲准離去。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有網民將2人「起底」，指王開辦小型補習社兼任職補習老師，伍婦則已為人母，育有年幼女兒，夫婦更曾就香港教育議題作出「出位」舉動，包括在去年6月出席立法會教育事務委員會，就小三基本能力評估（BCA，前稱TSA）的公聽會，當場撕毀TSA試卷及撒溪錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180104/bkn-20180104013334888-0104_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180104%2Fbkn-20180104013334888-0104_00822_001.html&d=UEqiDeshdO8W%2BcbXLZcSCgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=15ded072\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180104/bkn-20180104013334888-0104_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8864a65485cedac1f7c69e3448da2a5911364d38","tid":520001,"uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22221649_10155511021742254_667121978459525117_n.jpg?oh=482170a6a573993371f4ab68fd1a8812&amp;oe=5ABFAE2C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22221649_10155511021742254_667121978459525117_n.jpg%3Foh%3D482170a6a573993371f4ab68fd1a8812%26oe%3D5ABFAE2C&h=baceb1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSze Tat Chau<br />\n2017年10月7日 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n有眼利嘅益友發現，昨晚在銅鑼灣因上唔到巴士而發爛渣攔截新巴嘅柒頭，著住件「成功之前我們絕不放棄夢想」嘅熱狗tee。媽，好柒呀！"},{"pid":"dbcbacee9f0edce33819b546da87acdc47a4e57e","tid":520001,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c356303dadb53c107e30c1437dab28b3001e6445","tid":520001,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8864a65485cedac1f7c69e3448da2a5911364d38","tid":520001,"uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22221649_10155511021742254_667121978459525117_n.jpg?oh=482170a6a573993371f4ab68fd1a8812&amp;oe=5ABFAE2C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22221649_10155511021742254_667121978459525117_n.jpg%3Foh%3D482170a6a573993371f4ab68fd1a8812%26oe%3D5ABFAE2C&h=baceb1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSze Tat Chau<br />\n2017年10月7日 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n有眼利嘅益友發現，昨晚在銅鑼灣因上唔到巴士而發爛渣攔截新巴嘅柒頭，著住件「成功之前我們絕不放棄夢想」嘅熱狗tee。媽，好柒呀！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"熱民狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b0f459775e5aa94c1e0601120382741eb6a093","tid":520001,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"當值律師出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89614ba81858d5fa1eb8a5929b56d7aeb2aeaf9d","tid":520001,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d4b2651a300df355d46c5a40a13ba6e08671451","tid":520001,"uid":31990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"呢2件都比人拉<br />\n<br />\n咁果曰喺鵝頸橋因為架垃圾車定垃圾筒頂住個臭閪架車,死都唔肯走比人屌都扮無野坐喺車入面,搞到全cwb/跑馬地塞死晒果條臭閪都要比人拉至得喎"},{"pid":"3bc626fd3f0a5e9c4c24540d02b2a194911ae2c3","tid":520001,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbcbacee9f0edce33819b546da87acdc47a4e57e","tid":520001,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c422c4dbf894bb53b793330ba105be04f8a9c027","tid":520001,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方造成阻礙\t<br />\n任何人無合法權限或解釋而陳列或留下，或導致陳列或留下任何物品或東西，而這些物品或東西對在公眾地方的人或車輛造成阻礙、不便或危害者，或可能對在公眾地方的人或車輛造成阻礙、不便或危害者，<strong>可處罰款$5000或監禁3個月。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39985de5b7fb494d834053335715f5de8f417023","tid":520001,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e982e74d4828abb6f163bdbf0664b4139e5ab060","tid":520001,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"熱狗仔發動阻巴士戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得搵定當值律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155b448370564c7d9b4e63d957e15a1332e2a4ea","tid":520001,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/130110_052ae7e063dc1d86ad563b916571b583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F130110_052ae7e063dc1d86ad563b916571b583.jpg&h=65ad4d48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8274d996da1a7596b0f25f66cbafb9609ff624ec","tid":520001,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"人間垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}